      "height": 212.5914906315838,
      "text": "FUTURE PLATFORM VISION  —  OrgBlueprint as a Full SaaS Product\n\n  MONETISATION                  ECOSYSTEM                        INTELLIGENCE\n  Free tier: 3 blueprints/day   AppExchange listing               Fine-tuned model on SF data\n  Pro plan: $99/month           SI & partner white-label portal   RAG over Trailhead + SF docs\n  Enterprise: team seats        Embed in SF onboarding flows      Learns from 1000s of blueprints\n  Agency tier: client mgmt      API access for custom tooling     Predicts implementation risk\n\n  Multi-org management dashboard    |    Audit trail & compliance reports    |    Salesforce Identity SSO",
